  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      to test the metabolic and clinical effects of a 6-month program of dancing in subjects with
      type 2 diabetes and/or obesity, chronically cared for in two diabetes/metabolic units.
      Self-selection of the leisure time activity program was allowed to increase adherence to the
      physical activity programs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
